# Data & API agent

- JSON seeds in `data/seeds/` are the source of truth until Supabase is configured.
- `loadSeedRoadmaps()` is server-only (uses `fs`).
- API routes return seed data without env vars; Supabase is optional enhancement.
- Schema changes go in `supabase/schema.sql` with matching updates to `lib/types.ts`.
